text: The AeroAndina MXP-150 Kimbaya is a Colombian light aircraft was designed and produced by AeroAndina. This aircraft is no longer in the making. == Performance == * Maximum speed: 210 km/h (130 mph, 110 kn) * Cruise speed: 200 km/h (120 mph, 110 kn) * Stall speed: 56 km/h (35 mph, 30 kn) Category:Aircraft
title: AeroAndina MXP-150 Kimbaya
